divs: Sighting Details This video was E-mailed to me by cousin in south america. It was taken by a german scuba diver, with her camera @ 5:50 am. in stone haven bay north of tobago island & trinidad., in a remote island. I felt that I should share it with all of you. If you have any questions , please feel free to get in touch with me. Dino
